<https://example.org/smart-library-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://example.org/smart-library-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> "210316051 Kemal Mert Ceyhan; 190316073 Ahmet Burak Guvercin; 210316078 Khaled ALISMAIL"@en .
<https://example.org/smart-library-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-04-27"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://example.org/smart-library-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Version 0.2.0 of the Smart Library Loan Ontology. This phase extends the original circulation model with data acquisition provenance, topical enrichment, member profile signals, and recommendation-ready analytics for a smart library environment."@en .
